" Must of the time I compile neovim from source, because of that
" some CLI tools do not find neovim in my path in certain scenarios
" this file is only used as a very basic configuration to use
" vim instead of neovim on those tools, as vim is usually the default
" value for VISUAL and EDITOR environment variables


set number " enable line numbers
set relativenumber " enable relative line numbers


let &t_SI = "\e[5 q"   " Cursor to blinking bar in insert mode
let &t_SR = "\e[4 q"   " Cursor to underline in replace mode
let &t_EI = "\e[2 q"   " Cursor to block in normal mode
